    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir your <strong>ground allspice</strong> into the softened onion and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) and cook for 5-6 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
