        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook over a high heat for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite, then drain and return to the pot</p><p>While the bulgur wheat is cooking, dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
