            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince has browned, stir in your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and reduce the heat to medium-low</p><p>Cook for 6-7 min or until thick and reduced to a chilli-like consistency – this is your<strong> Mexican-Style meat-free mince chilli</strong></p>",
