    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> diced apple</strong> to the<strong> quick-pickled red onion</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>apple salsa</strong></p><p>Fluff the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>bulgur</strong> with a fork and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
