      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Mexican-Style meat-free mince chilli</strong> over the <strong>fluffed bulgur </strong>with the <strong>apple salsa</strong> to the side</p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
